_sText:
Rnd_virtualarena - Random Aimmap

2-32 Player

Simple Room with Cubes for cover and separate
start Areas for each Team. Cubes are at the
start of each round randomly distributed.

All Players start each round with the same equipment;
Assaultsuit, Knife, a P228 and one of the
following randomly selected Weapons:
M4a1, Ak47, Mp5, P90, sg552, M3 or a Fraggrenade.

30 seconds after roundstart, all remaining Players
in the start Area will be struck by lightning,
also all the doors to the main Room only open from
outside.
